<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>Cool, might have to get this one. The image is interesting, but all the type needs help. The title is whispering, and the fonts don&#8217;t really match very well.</p>
<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Bonnie Ferrante</font> submitted <strong>Leya</strong> designed by Bonnie Ferrante. &#8220;In a world where eye color may determine your future, Leya is born with one green and one blue eye.&#8221;<br />
