<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Connie Chastain</font> submitted <strong>Love in Smallfoot Alley</strong> designed by Connie Chastain. &#8220;Smallfoot Alley is an area of rural Chatahoula County in Alabama known for infrequent sightings of Bigfoot-like cryptids, except they&#8217;re less than five feet tall, and thus are known as the Smallfoot. The road on the cover is the location of a Smallfoot sighting that opens the story.&#8221;<br />
