<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>Glad I didn&#8217;t get to see the rest. This one just defeats me. &#8220;The Way of All Flesh&#8221;? Seriously? Maybe I&#8217;ll call my next book &#8220;Remembrance of Things Past.&#8221; No, maybe &#8220;Paradise Lost.&#8221; The images clearly don&#8217;t belong together and make little sense, and the added-in eye color on the guy in the corner is so obviously fake it makes you suspect this is a parody of some kind. Unless that&#8217;s the effect you were going for, I suggest hiring one of the talented designers whose work you see in this post.</p>
