<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Donna Joy</font> submitted <strong>Tangible Illusions</strong> designed by Donna Joy. &#8220;Tangible Illusions takes the reader on a journey of emotions through seven poems and a short story. The works deal with loss and loneliness. The picture is from Unsplash.&#8221;<br />
