<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Gene Bathurst</font> submitted <strong>Magnum Thrax and the Amusement Park of Doom</strong> designed by Gene Bathurst. &#8220;Wanted something that was loud and clear when a teeny tiny thumbnail.&#8221;<br />
