<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>You&#8217;re almost there. But there are simply too many figures, at too great a distance. Great illustration style, but I would &#8220;zoom&#8221; in so we can really engage with them.</p>
<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Georgina Titmus</font> submitted <strong>Chicken Nugget Run!</strong> designed by Georgina Titmus. &#8220;e-published under my pseudonym Ali Aardwolff &#8211; I designed this cover combining my own artwork with the technical assistance of Powerpoint.&#8221;<br />
