<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>A lesson: when you use an image of this sexy, exotic woman with overtones of bondage and slavery, please don&#8217;t pick a font that belongs on an invitation to a Valentine&#8217;s Day party.</p>
<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Grier Cooper</font> submitted <strong>WISH: Indigo Dreams Series #1</strong> designed by LJ Anderson, Mayhem Cover Creations. &#8220;Original photo of ballet dancer © Grier Cooper (author)&#8221;<br />
