<p><font color="darkred">Ioana Visan</font> submitted <strong>Broken People</strong> designed by Cristina Birtea. &#8220;The prosthetic arm belongs to the Golden Lady, one of the main characters in the novel, and the pattern on the sphere is meant to imply she holds the fate of the whole world in her hand. The illustrator drew exactly what I asked her, so if anything doesn&#8217;t work, it&#8217;s on me.&#8221;<br />
