<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>Although the &#8220;engraving&#8221; of the orc and the bill details is obviously very skillful, this doesn&#8217;t, in the end, really look much like a book cover.</p>
<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">James Duprie</font> submitted <strong>The Leopard Rider</strong> designed by Dave Fymbo from Limelightbookcovers. &#8220;Title relates to a character in this historical fiction novel.&#8221;<br />
