<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>Shows both the advantages and disadvantages of &#8220;template&#8221; book covers. While you don&#8217;t have to worry about it looking very amateurish, it may not suit your book that well either. I&#8217;ve never seen a challah with seeds on it, creating a bit of dissonance.</p>
