<p><font color="darkred">Jenny B. Jones</font> submitted <strong>A Sugar Creek Christmas</strong> designed by Kelli Standish. &#8220;For this cover, we wanted to capture the small town, Southern setting, the warmth of the holidays, and a slightly differently look for the typical couple on the cover.&#8221;<br />
