<p><font color="darkred">Jenny B. Jones</font> submitted <strong>Can&#8217;t Let You Go</strong> designed by Kelli Standish. &#8220;Can&#8217;t Let You Go is a New Adult romance, but we wanted to try something a little different and break from trend for the cover.&#8221;<br />
