<p><font color="darkred">Katharina Gerlach</font> submitted <strong>The Dwarf and the Twins (Treasures Retold #1)</strong> designed by myself. &#8220;The other covers in the series follow the same concept (black silhouettes against a blue sky)&#8221;<br />
