<p><font color="darkred">Margaret Lesh</font> submitted <strong>Mr. Katz is a Zombie</strong> designed by Steven Lesh. &#8220;This lower middle grade book is designed for readers age 8 to 12. Because of the book&#8217;s humorous bent&#8211;think The Hardy Boys meets Ghostbusters&#8211;I wanted the cover to have more of a fun cartoon feel than grotesque imagery that so many of the zombie-themed books have.&#8221;<br />
