<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Mary Ann Vitale</font> submitted <strong>The Water Lily Fairy</strong> designed by Susan Shorter. &#8220;The Water Lily Fairy is walking on the lily pads, ready to discover the little world around her.&#8221;<br />
