<p><font color="darkred">Melinda Martin</font> submitted <strong>Peacock Swamp | The Nine</strong> designed by Melinda Martin. &#8220;Moths are an element of this story that tie in with the main character. I chose a few images of some moths and then overlapped them in the shape of a 9 and applied shading and highlighting. I then added a light effect inside the 9.&#8221;<br />
